                "post_type": "page",
                "content_format": "blocks",
                "content": "<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":2} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Summer Cookout Plan</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Join your neighbors for a relaxed summer cookout in the park. We'll fire up the grill, share potluck sides, and enjoy an easy afternoon of food, games, and good company. Bring a chair, your favorite dish to pass, and an appetite.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Confirm headcount and assign potluck dishes one week ahead.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Pick up burgers, buns, drinks, ice, and charcoal the day before.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Set up tables, grill, and trash bins one hour before guests arrive.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n</ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\">\n<!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"#menu\">View menu</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->"
            }
        }
    ],
